        <para>
            The results of these equations are clamped to the range 
                        <inlineequation><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
                            <!-- eqn: [0,1]: -->
